Who are you

6
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:50,320
to judge Yulin's Pinsanxian?

7
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:53,000
Mister,

8
00:00:53,399 --> 00:00:54,840
may I know

9
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:56,359
if this is the 40th Li Lamb Restaurant?

10
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:57,920
You are heading in the wrong direction.

11
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:01,799
Young man, you need to practice more.

12
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:04,079
Isn't this Mr. Wang?

13
00:01:04,079 --> 00:01:06,560
He is the successor
to Yulin's Pinsanxian recipe.

14
00:01:06,599 --> 00:01:07,079
Master,

15
00:01:07,079 --> 00:01:09,239
I thought you were not taking part
in the program.

16
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:10,439
