17
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,079
Not bad.

18
00:01:23,439 --> 00:01:26,439
Kid, you seasoned the soup well.

19
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:29,439
It's tangy and spicy. It's delicious.

20
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:32,280
Thank you for your compliment.

21
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:35,159
Linda made this.

22
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:37,879
I'll take care of this.

23
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:46,439
What on earth is this?

24
00:01:46,439 --> 00:01:47,840
It's both fishy and greasy.

25
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,560
The meatballs are falling apart.

26
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,760
It's a complete mess.

27
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:55,000
Is this what you claimed

28
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,159
to be authentic?

29
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,400
Master,

30
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,799
Ms. Linda is a celebrity.

31
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,760
Her company wants to invest
in my restaurant.

32
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,599
I'm doing this for the business.

33
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:09,960
Good, well done.

34
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,840
You do things without a clear conscience

35
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:15,680
just for the sake of good business.

36
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,360
I don't have a disciple like you.

37
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,159
No conscience.

38
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:22,400
Get out of the way.

39
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:24,960
Shame on you.

40
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:31,360
In Yulin's Pinsanxian tradition,

41
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:34,039
there have never been strict rules.

42
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:35,800
Whether it's authentic or not,

43
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,599
the people of Yulin have the final say.

44
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,159
- That's right.
- He's right.

45
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,400
So whose dish is the most authentic?

46
